title: Daniel Austin from Die Young
itunes:title: Daniel Austin from Die Young
description:
The Vegan Meathead, Daniel Austin, joins the podcast today. Daniel is the vocalist from hardcore band Die Young and a prolific author of books, poetry and his first work of fiction entitled Cane Field. We discuss weightlifting, writing and DIY touring. Enjoy!
